News Releases, Media Advisories

October 23, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
MISSOURI REPUBLICAN STATE COMMITEE ? FEDERAL COMMITTEE
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Missouri Republican State Committee ? Federal Committee. This audit covers the period of January 1, 1999 through December 31, 2000.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: Final Audit Report on Missouri Republican State Committee-Federal Committee is Available
